 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"your head\", \"from\": 2957, \"to\": 2966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will come in navy, black and gray, sizes S to 3XL.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"navy\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"$529,galvingreen.com There are so many great golf and leisure pieces to look forward to this year from Ralph Lauren, but the biggest new feature to look for is all the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s polos have stitched-in collars.\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.8130685942828848, \"rank\": 0.22990853051169144, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many great golf and leisure pieces\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest new feature\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3204}, {\"ngram\": \"all the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s polos\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"collars\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This ensures the collar holds its shape, and when worn with a sweater or crewneck over top, it still looks sharp no matter what.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the collar\", \"from\": 3282, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"its shape\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3308}, {\"ngram\": \"a sweater\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3338}, {\"ngram\": \"crewneck\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 3356, \"to\": 3359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also the prints have been quieted down and made smaller, making them more versatile and easy to wear especially transitioning on and off the golf course to m